views.markdown: If you need help with "oyster", you can contact Steve Sarmiento, the developer, via e-mail.
Steve Sarmiento is the maintainer of the package "oyster". Please contact them via email for any questions on this version of the package.
If you found a mistake in the depiction or cannot download the package, you can reach out to the maintainer of the "StevSarm's Repo" repo, Steve Sarmiento.
